***************************** Hooks *****************************
1. useState - Allow a functional component to use component level state
2. useEffect - Allow a functional component to use 'lifecycle methods'
3. useContext - Allow a functional component to use the context system
4. useRef - Allow a functional component to use the ref system
5. useReducer -  Allow a functional component to store data through a reducer

and more .... 

6. const [currentValue,setCurrentValue] = useState(initialValue);


